      "text": "API\n\nEmails\n\nPOST /api/v1/messages\nGET /api/v1/messages/{id}\n\nFolders\nGET /api/v1/folders\nGET /api/v1/folders/{id}\nGET / api/v1/folders/{id}/messages\n\nfolders = all, inbox, primary, spam, deleted etc",
