      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Options :\nRelational : x\nObject store : maybe\nNoSQL : yes\n- Scalable\n- optimised for write\n- tunable for read\n\n\nSelected NoSQL like cassandra\ngmail used bigtable",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Options :\nRelational : x\nObject store : maybe\nNoSQL : yes\n- Scalable\n- optimised for write\n- tunable for read\n\n\nSelected NoSQL like cassandra\ngmail used bigtable",
      "autoResize": true,
