      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bIb",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 566038514,
      "version": 542,
      "versionNonce": 816335598,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782643885110,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Access paterns\n1. get all folder by user\n2. Get all emails by a user and folder\n3. Get a particular email by user and folder \n4. Create, dleete and Get email by a folder\n5. emails by read/ unread by user\n\nTables\n\nFolders_by_user\nuser_id (PK)\nfolder_id \nfolder_name \nsequence (CK asc)\n\n\nemails_by_folder_user\nuser_id (PK)\nfolder_id (PK)\nemail_id TIMEUUID ( CK DESC)\nfrom\nto\ntext\nattachment boolean\nheader\nsubject\nbody\n\nemails_read and emails_unread \nuser_id (PK)\nfolder_id (PK)\nemail_id TIMEUUID ( CK DESC)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Access paterns\n1. get all folder by user\n2. Get all emails by a user and folder\n3. Get a particular email by user and folder \n4. Create, dleete and Get email by a folder\n5. emails by read/ unread by user\n\nTables\n\nFolders_by_user\nuser_id (PK)\nfolder_id \nfolder_name \nsequence (CK asc)\n\n\nemails_by_folder_user\nuser_id (PK)\nfolder_id (PK)\nemail_id TIMEUUID ( CK DESC)\nfrom\nto\ntext\nattachment boolean\nheader\nsubject\nbody\n\nemails_read and emails_unread \nuser_id (PK)\nfolder_id (PK)\nemail_id TIMEUUID ( CK DESC)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
