      "updated": 1782644693971,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Search :\noptions \n1. Elastic search\n2. LSM tree based custom search\n\nas we use cassandra we can build more tables on top of LSM \ntree to support 2nd use case\npros:\nsingle datastore\nno duplicates\nfull control\n\n",
